Series

Write a program to generate the following series 

Sample Input:

5

Sample Output:

3  2  11  14  27
CODING:
import java.util.Scanner;
class Series
{
    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
        int x=sc.nextInt();
        
        for (int i=1;i<=x;i++)
       {
        if(i%2==0)
        {
            System.out.println(i*i-2);
        }
        else
        System.out.println(i*i+2);
       }
    }    
}
